WEBVTT

00:00.522 --> 00:02.125
<i>Previously on</i> The Vampire Diaries...

00:02.150 --> 00:04.296
STEFAN: <i>I really hoped that
when we put Sybil down,</i>

00:04.321 --> 00:06.201
<i>it'd break whatever
control she had over him,</i>

00:06.226 --> 00:07.539
<i>but she still has ahold of him.</i>

00:07.564 --> 00:10.238
Turn off your humanity,
pledge your loyalty to me.

00:10.263 --> 00:12.530
If anyone can pull me back
from the precipice, it's you.

00:12.532 --> 00:13.543
I know you can.

00:13.568 --> 00:15.833
There are two of us and
you've met my sister,

00:15.835 --> 00:18.102
- Seline.
- Seline is the other siren?

00:18.104 --> 00:20.171
You're assuming that I'm
gonna let you remember this

00:20.173 --> 00:21.572
<i>when you wake up.</i>

00:21.574 --> 00:23.726
Your intern, Georgie,
she broke into the house.

00:23.751 --> 00:25.443
<i>I mean, she's just
a little weirdo, right?</i>

00:25.445 --> 00:26.410
- Georgie.
- I'm here.

00:26.412 --> 00:28.946
- Sorry.
- Wait!

00:28.948 --> 00:30.414
Why did you make me do that? (gasps)

00:30.416 --> 00:34.252
By the way, send Cade my regards.

00:34.254 --> 00:35.651
(tines humming)

00:35.676 --> 00:37.476
If this disrupts your psychic ability,

00:37.501 --> 00:39.350
<i>then why is Damon still your puppet?</i>

00:39.375 --> 00:41.408
I gave him a look at what awaits him,

00:41.433 --> 00:44.539
and even that was enough to make
him flip his humanity switch.

00:44.564 --> 00:46.430
Damon believes in hell.

00:46.432 --> 00:48.686
I ripped into Tyler's throat last night.

00:48.711 --> 00:50.944
Humanity or not, nobody
would forgive you for that.

00:58.376 --> 01:00.643
