01:23.469 --> 01:25.570
♪ Nothing else matters ♪

01:25.572 --> 01:28.172
♪ In a moment ♪

01:28.174 --> 01:32.143
♪ You've lived before ♪

01:33.846 --> 01:36.681
♪ It's over now ♪

01:36.683 --> 01:38.883
(phone buzzes)

01:39.786 --> 01:42.793
♪ It's over now ♪

01:44.057 --> 01:47.692
(children laughing)

01:47.694 --> 01:52.163
♪ Another day without my shadow ♪

01:52.165 --> 01:54.165
(bad British accent):
Mmm. Why, I do declare,

01:54.167 --> 01:57.278
this is some of the best
purple tea I've ever had.

01:57.303 --> 01:59.136
- (slurping) Mmm.
- (laughing)

01:59.138 --> 02:00.404
(phone rings)

02:00.406 --> 02:05.676
♪ Looking for flowers in the dirt ♪

02:19.125 --> 02:21.325
